========================
JAVA PROGRAM
========================

1.  javac -Xlint Kosaraju.java

    Note that the Xlint option is required because I am using an array of ArrayList's.

2.  java -Xss3m Kosaraju

    Note the -Xss3m option.
    This specifies the stack size for the program.
    The default stack size is just not enough for the huge number of DFS recursions and throws a StackOverflowError.



=======================
PYTHON PROGRAM
=======================

1.  $ ulimit -s 800000

    This sets the stack size for the program.
    The default stack size is just not enough for the huge number of DFS recursions and gives segmentation fault.

2.  python kos.py    
